title: Families of Israel music festivalgoers are beginning to learn their loved ones are among the dead
description: For four days Hannie Ricardo held out hope that her daughter Oriya was in hiding after Hamas terrorists descended upon a music festival in the Israel desert on Saturday morning, killing hundreds.

title: ‘We’re not Hamas’: Gaza residents say airstrikes are putting civilians in grave danger
description: Residents describe devastation and panic as Israel’s bombardment of the Gaza Strip continues after Hamas attacks spurred Israel into war with the militant group.

title: Israel-Hamas war discourse shows the increasingly fraught nature of online speech
description: People on the internet are debating what online activism and solidarity look like amid the Israel-Hamas war. They’re having trouble agreeing.

title: Utah TikTok lawsuit alleges harm to teen users
description: Gov. Spencer Cox and Attorney General Sean Reyes announced the state of Utah has filed a consumer protection lawsuit against TikTok, arguing the social media platform harms teen users. KSL reports.
